content: Dont waste your 99 pence or cents or whatever
Its an app it's about heritage,what's not like?
Can't get into any other articles besides the front page.
Never had a problem. Interesting stories.
I look at this app almost every day . I am a n amateur archaeologist and love this app for the breadth of its stories.
Knowledgeable. Belle ui. Smoothly. Easy access.
Woah, my antivirus scanner tagged this app as potentially unwanted, and when I check, lots of unnecessary permissions. Think I'll pass. Uninstalled without opening.
Well written and up to date with latest discoveries and research.

I love being able to keep up with the latest archaeology, history, and science news. Its located in one place with an archive that goes back years with neatly sorted categories. Very helpful. I just wish there was a way to better sort by date to read older articles first, especially in your 'read later' section.
Great app with updates, this really deserves more attention!

Update: Thank you for taking the suggestion of changing the font. Now I just wish you had more new stories as I love to read about history! Awesome app!   I love this app BUT the font makes it a little difficult to read, thus I don't read it as much as I want to. 5 stars if the font is easier to read because I would read a LOT more!
It is worth more then 99¢ Thanks for spending the time to put this all together
Definitely the best archaeology app I've seen on the play store. Well done! :)
